  "detailed_description": "Description:<br />\r\nAn eternal slasher & shooter game. Ugly enemies, awesome bosses and tons of dark humor.<br />\r\nYou can slice your enemies with a fork, splatter them with a machine gun or simply mash 'em up with a flashlight.<br />\r\nThe plot of Tomato Way 3 takes place between the events of Tomato Way 1 and 2. <br />\r\nKnowing the story of the other two parts is unnecessary yet recommendable.<br />\r\nIt's a grandiose end to the game series about a tomato hungry for some meat.",
